text: Gila Helena Bergqvist Ulfung (born Gila Helena Hasson 28 November 1967 in Brännkyrka) is a Swedish producer, television presenter and actress. She is best known for her role in the Ronny and Ragge series Byhåla which was broadcast on SVT from 1991 to 1993. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people
title: Gila Bergqvist
